  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FC69A2E0-18A7-0135-1363-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Chat is a course tool that is available to all students in the course. Chats cannot be limited to specific students. </p>
<p>Instructors can use the chat tool to allow students to contact them when online, create virtual office hours, conduct group discussions or study sessions. </p>
<p>All users in the course can also access the chat history. </p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> Students cannot delete chat comments.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
